6ï¸âƒ£ Security & Best Practices
Security Implications

Archives may contain sensitive internal data

Must be:

Owned by root

Not world-writable

Transferred securely if moved off-server

Why this approach is recommended

Non-destructive

Auditable

Reversible

Aligns with enterprise backup practices

